text: Go On is a NBC sitcom series that aired from 8 August 2012 to 11 April 2013 for one season and twenty-two episodes. It starred Matthew Perry, Laura Benanti, Julie White, Allison Miller, John Cho, Tonita Castro and Tyler James Williams. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:2012 American television series debuts Category:2013 American television series endings Category:NBC network series
